title: Honey Butter Dduk Recipe (Korean Rice Cake)
description:
How to Make Honey Butter Cheese Dduk (Korean Rice Cake) 

In this video, we will show you how to make honey butter cheese dduk (korean rice cake).  It’s easy!  At the end I’ll show you a new discovery that I made in Korea, and during the last 8 mins of the video, you can watch some fireworks over Seoul for the 4th of July.

If you love Korean honey butter fried chicken, you will love this recipe.  Koreans seem to love honey butter flavor because I see it everywhere - from almonds, to chips, even to dried squid.
